{
  "title": "DynamicSLM: Capability-Modular, Self-Improving Small Language Models for AIKernel",
  "upload_type": "publication",
  "publication_type": "technicalnote",
  "description": "This technical note proposes DynamicSLM, a capability-modular and self-improving small language model architecture for AIKernel. DynamicSLM defines model artifacts through an AIKernel Model ABI and enables dynamic capability loading, capability-level differential distillation, hot-swappable runtime scheduling, and ReplayLog-backed lineage verification under AIKernel governance. This work is conceptual and architectural in nature; it does not present empirical benchmarks. The English manuscript is canonical; the Japanese manuscript is included as a companion translation.",
